fields.name: Bearded Tit
fields.description:
Bearded Tit painted in watercolour.

This is painted on A5 size 100% cotton, acid-free, cold-pressed, 300gsm, archival watercolour paper by Saunders Waterford. 

I use professional quality paints that are lightfast tested. 

Item is not framed.

fields.name: Blue Tit (print)
fields.description:
A cute Bluetit perched on a twig.
Gallery-grade print on high-quality paper, this is the real deal.
Lightly textured 100% cotton paper.
Custom sizes, based on artwork dimensions. 
Dimensions include a 1 - 2 inch (2.5 - 5.0cm) white border to assist in framing.
Large prints shipped in tubes, small & medium prints in protective flat mailers.

fields.name: Blue Tit Clock
fields.description:
It's always art o'clock when your clock is a work of art.
Printed polypropylene face made for you when you order.
Metal hands.
Bamboo wood frame in natural finish.
Quartz clock mechanism for accurate timekeeping.
Clear plexiglass lens.
Built-in rear hook, ready to hang.
AA battery not included.

fields.name: Blue Tit Classic T-Shirt
fields.description:
The standard, traditional t-shirt for everyday wear.
Classic, generous, boxy fit.
Male model shown is 6'0" / 183 cm tall and wearing size Medium.
Female model shown is 5'8" / 173 cm tall and wearing size Small.
Heavyweight 5.3 oz / 180 gsm fabric, 100% preshrunk cotton.
Double-needle hems and neck band for durability.
